scripts/env-setup.sh.message:
the idea is to provide whatever link, path or version you want
for example for git something like:
ANSIBLE_PIP_VERSION='git+https://github.com/ansible/ansible.git@{branch}'

Or we allow overriding in two ways:

ANSIBLE_PIP_VERSION=${ANSIBLE_PIP_VERSION:-'!=2.8.9,<2.9'}
ANSIBLE_PIP_STRING=${ANSIBLE_PIP_STRING:-ansible${ANSIBLE_PIP_VERSION}}

Might be nice to also break out the default version to make updates to it clearer:

DEFAULT_ANSIBLE_PIP_VERSION='!=2.8.9,<2.9'

